# ---- ITS I-95: raw source (2.3 GB) AND the extracted sample are LOCAL-ONLY ----
# The extracted sample derives from INRIX TMC (tmc_speed_15min.csv) + VDOT sensors (sensor_15min.csv) +
# probe trips/waypoints — all restricted by the never-commit rule. It is rendered locally for the flagship
